    a: 'Yes. We install complete central AC systems for new Laveen homes, including proper Manual J heat load calculations to ensure the system is sized for your specific home — not just what the builder specced to minimize cost. If you are building or have a newly built home and want an honest assessment of whether the builder-installed system is right-sized, call <a href="tel:+17605941125">(760) 594-1125</a>.'
