  {
    q: 'Do you handle commercial refrigeration in Laveen?',
    a: 'Yes. As Laveen\'s commercial sector develops along Dobbins Road and 51st Avenue, restaurants, grocery operations, and food businesses are opening and need commercial refrigeration service. We provide walk-in cooler repair, commercial refrigeration installation, and 24/7 emergency refrigeration response for Laveen businesses. Call for service.'
