      <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> → Locations → Laveen, AZ</p>
      <h1>AC Repair in Laveen, AZ — Altered Air</h1>
      <p>
        AC repair in Laveen, AZ is something Altered Air does regularly — and we are one of the
        few West Valley contractors who actually prioritize this area. Laveen is about 30–35 minutes
        from our Buckeye base, sitting at the foot of South Mountain along Dobbins Road. The
        community has grown dramatically in recent years, producing thousands of new homes with
        builder-grade HVAC systems that are now reaching the summer heat tests that reveal
